summary: Replaces leather armor with Linwe\'s armor
descriptionHtml:
Replaces the graphics for leather armor, leather bracers, leather boots & leather helmet with the graphics used by Linwe\'s armor set, also used as a non-wearable set of armor by several members of the thieves guild.

Works with male & female, all races.

Does not suffer from the \'missing arms syndrome\' of original Linwe\'s armor.

Hood inventory graphic is highly reflective for some reason (if you know why, let me know so I can correct it).

Installation: Extract archive to \\skyrim\\data\\meshes\\armor\\
author: QuickFox
